project_descr: The setting up of a structure to administer NHI and developing the framework for the establishment of NHI; the setting up of a NHI secretariat within the Ministry of health to prepare for the launch of NHI in Grenada.

outputs.output_descr:
National Health Insurance, the vehicle to provide individuals and
families with necessary health benefits without sacrificing other areas of
life or worrying about forcing them back into poverty.
